peuvent avoir besoin</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de Dapoxetine</span> <span class="hps">120 mg</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">s'ils</span> <span class="hps">n'ont pas r&eacute;pondus &agrave;</span> <span class="hps">l'original.</span><br /><br /> <span class="hps">Demandez &agrave; votre m&eacute;decin</span> <span class="hps">toutes les questions</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">que vous pouvez avoir</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; propos de</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'utilisation</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de Dapoxetine</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong><span class="long_text" lang="fr">CONSERVATION</span></strong></p><p><span id="result_box" class="long_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ce m&eacute;dicament</span> <span class="hps">doit &ecirc;tre conserv&eacute; &agrave;</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la temp&eacute;rature ambiante</span> <span class="hps">loin de la chaleur</span><span>, de la lumi&egrave;re</span> <span class="hps">et de l'humidit&eacute;</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Gardez ce m&eacute;dicament</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">hors de la port&eacute;e des enfants</span><span class="hps alt-edited">.</span></span></p><p><strong><span lang="fr">INFORMATION ADDITIVE:</span></strong></p><p><span id="result_box" class="long_text short_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ingr&eacute;dient actif:</span> <span class="hps">chlorhydrate de</span> <span class="hps">Dapoxetine</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE S&Eacute;CURIT&Eacute;</strong></p><p><strong><span id="result_box" class="long_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">N'utilisez pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Dapoxetine si</span>:</span></strong></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" class="long_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous &ecirc;tes allergique</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&agrave; un ingr&eacute;dient de</span> <span class="hps">Dapoxetine</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box